; Political satire example using documented Friedrich Merz memes and recurring topics.
; It deliberately avoids demeaning or disputed migration quotes.
.entry main

main:
  push "Was ist Bubatz?"
  merz "THE CRITIC SAYS"

  push "Jetzt darf auch mal Rambo Zambo im Adenauer-Haus sein."
  merz "THE CRITIC SAYS"

  push "Bierdeckel-Steuer"
  merz "THE CRITIC SAYS"

  push "Brandmauer"
  merz "THE CRITIC SAYS"

  push "Mehr arbeiten"
  merz "THE CRITIC SAYS"

  halt
